"using their credit or debit cards within the store. The payment form is "
"securely embedded on the website, ensuring a seamless and user-friendly "
"experience for buyers. <br/><br/><strong>Requirements:</"
"strong><ul><li>Before enabling this option, please contact Przelewy24 to "
"activate the necessary services on your account.</li><li>Ensure your store "
